      "time_str": "00:09.850",
      "text": "是故意的吗",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 12.65,
      "time_str": "00:12.650",
      "text": "是我得罪谁了吗",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 15.2,
      "time_str": "00:15.200",
      "text": "这一天竟然每件事情都失算",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 20.62,
      "time_str": "00:20.620",
      "text": "只想转个弯",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 23.12,
      "time_str": "00:23.120",
      "text": "却绕到了飞机场",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 25.87,
      "time_str": "00:25.870",
      "text": "发现没钱在身上",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 32.4,
      "time_str": "00:32.400",
      "text": "乌云乌云快走开",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 34.47,
      "time_str": "00:34.470",
      "text": "你可知道我不常带把伞 带把伞啊",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 42.42,
      "time_str": "00:42.420",
      "text": "乌云乌云快走开",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 45.17,
      "time_str": "00:45.170",
      "text": "感觉你在挑战我的乐观 的乐观",
